{"tid":545441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"淫照風暴　神秘人逐張上網　越演越烈","createTime":"2018-01-30T13:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T14:38:29.000Z","uid":49974,"like":275,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":128,"replies":[{"pid":"cf06900097f0d758ce1c18eab052bed6d90e82b6","tid":545441,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T13:36:42.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】娛樂圈淫穢照片風暴橫掃互聯網，捲入的女星與淫照越傳越多。經神秘網民「事先張揚」，兩幀疑似張芝的裸照昨在網絡廣傳；五幅被指是陳冠希（ Edison）與鍾欣桐（阿嬌）的「連環圖」式情慾照接出現，完全按照「預告」逐張上載至互聯網。繼阿嬌後，陳冠希和張芝的公司昨已報警求助。警方商業罪案調查科科技罪案組探員正手揪出發放照片的神秘網民。記者：陳月媚、雷子樂<br />\n<br />\n淫照風暴昨如網上「連續劇」般，按神秘網民率先預告的「劇本」上演。神秘人本周日已「放風」，指即將會流傳張芝的淫照。「預言」昨日凌晨12時30分應驗，相中人只穿一件極性感上衣，雙眼半合作自慰狀。約下午6時，網上再現另一張疑似是芝在廁所拍下的全裸照，似是有鋪排的惡意行為。<br />\n神秘人本周日率先發放的一張被指是陳冠希和鍾欣桐床上淫照，前日被網民質疑其真偽。發相人似有意回應網上輿論，昨午2時許再度發放連續五張同一場景的連環淫照。該批相片檔案細小，似從錄影帶片段中撮取。<br />\n淫照出現哄動各大互聯網討論區，中港台多個熱門網站昨日都出現網絡擠塞，甚至癱瘓。神秘網民其後再發出「預告」，聲言將發放一條長達10多分鍾的性愛短片，但至昨晚片段未有出現。另外，網民又曾預告將發放其餘多名女星的淫照，也未見於互聯網。<br />\n<br />\n神秘人上載照片時間<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20080130/large/30la1p101new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20080130%2Flarge%2F30la1p101new.jpg&h=ab4bf6b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n29/1　2:00pm<br />\n(圖片經本報剪裁)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20080130/large/30la1p102new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20080130%2Flarge%2F30la1p102new.jpg&h=32a990b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n29/1　12:30am<br />\n(圖片經本報剪裁)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20080130/large/30la1p103new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20080130%2Flarge%2F30la1p103new.jpg&h=f3274f73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n28/1　3:00pm<br />\n(圖片經本報剪裁)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20080130/large/30la1p104new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20080130%2Flarge%2F30la1p104new.jpg&h=da1c5af0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n27/1　8:30pm<br />\n(圖片經本報剪裁)"},{"pid":"68f7da7b72cf67bd5b89e20e2e645d033d3267b7","tid":545441,"uid":49974,"like":24,"dislike":4,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T13:36:47.000Z","msg":"陳冠希今赴美　向女友解釋<br />\n<br />\n事件令娛樂圈人人自危，陳冠希所屬的紅館經理人公司老闆林建岳親自介入，請來大律師胡漢清擔任法律顧問，並勒令 Edison暫時休假，要求他回公司與律師開會。晚上8時許，紅館發言人梁小姐透露已就淫照事件報警，並指事態嚴重，過份渲染色情，已尋求演藝人協會協助。<br />\n紅館負責人管小姐接受本報查詢時說：「 Edison由家到2月中會一路放假，大約20幾號先會做唱片宣傳，暫時佢工作冇受到任何影響，廣告商都冇打過投訴。」<br />\n但據悉，事件對陳冠希造成很大打擊，消息指他很擔心女友楊永晴（ Vincy）的反應，計劃今日飛往美國波士頓向女友解釋事件始末，並在當地逗留約兩個星期才回港。<br />\n張芝發聲明：無良不道德<br />\n事件中最新受害人張芝昨日透過律師行發表聲明稱：「就近日在互聯網上有不法份子發放及流傳疑似張小姐的不雅相片，張小姐強烈譴責該等不法行為實屬無良、不道德、不負責任及惡作劇」。聲明指張芝的經理人已向警方報案，亦保留所有權利，向有關發放、上載或轉載之人士追究法律負任。<br />\n鍾欣桐的經理人公司英皇娛樂集團昨再次發表聲明，堅持有關不雅照片是以移花接木手法製作。阿嬌的經理人霍汶希昨表示，公司要員會和律師、警方保持緊密聯絡，盡量低調處理事件，不想讓惡作劇的人得逞，她說：「每日有唔同版本出現，我唔會再回應。」霍又表示鍾欣桐病倒，但與淫照事件無關。她接受商台訪問時稱，未有收過任何勒索電話。"},{"pid":"091e0bf18ed0dc87fdfe5c84c87a6180b21a9eba","tid":545441,"uid":49974,"like":31,"dislike":4,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T13:37:28.000Z","msg":"捲入事件藝人反應<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20080130/large/30la1p1new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20080130%2Flarge%2F30la1p1new.jpg&h=c9058db3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳冠希（27歲）<br />\n<br />\n態度：未評論淫照真偽，只稱網上流傳不雅照片為「惡作劇」<br />\n<br />\n行動：昨日已就淫照事件報警，之前稱不排除法律行動追究<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20080130/large/30la1p2new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20080130%2Flarge%2F30la1p2new.jpg&h=50e7ebb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鍾欣桐（27歲）<br />\n<br />\n態度：經理人公司兩度發表聲明，堅持涉及鍾欣桐的淫照為「移花接木」製作<br />\n<br />\n行動：前日已就淫照事件報警，之前稱不排除法律行動追究<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20080130/large/30la1p3new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20080130%2Flarge%2F30la1p3new.jpg&h=91693472&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳文媛（28歲）<br />\n<br />\n態度：不回應事件<br />\n<br />\n行動：不回應事件<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20080130/large/30la1p4new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20080130%2Flarge%2F30la1p4new.jpg&h=b85221f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張栢芝（27歲）<br />\n<br />\n態度：未評論淫照真偽，只透過聲明以「疑似張小姐的不雅照片」形容淫照<br />\n<br />\n行動：其經理人已就事件報警備案，保留法律追究權利"},{"pid":"c4be3c6598b223278eb89169646acefa2c1f1b6a","tid":545441,"uid":6674,"like":583,"dislike":1,"score":582,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T13:43:13.000Z","msg":"十年又過去 舉止仍像少女"},{"pid":"4bc04741135a953a3c55877e3cee1b228372cf93","tid":545441,"uid":53498,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T13:52:20.000Z","msg":"啲相假嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c959e92fcd5c5e84bcbc9a82ad5a447fff9b036","tid":545441,"uid":1713,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T13:52:59.000Z","msg":"奇拿巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7acb29932623756204dd902fd0a4bacc821bdfd8","tid":545441,"uid":59832,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T13:53:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">年又過年</span></span>"},{"pid":"aaf0369919277b43b0744c14a557978db6922199","tid":545441,"uid":97708,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T13:55:17.000Z","msg":"漢堡神偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b8045e368b78184af34ddb73b350d3f5ef19ab","tid":545441,"uid":59832,"like":636,"dislike":5,"score":631,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/213029_493e84016489d49f61dac705e5204a37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F213029_493e84016489d49f61dac705e5204a37.jpg&h=4712ce7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"353ad5b6cf4584ec47a70655493769fc55775838","tid":545441,"uid":38049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:04:14.000Z","msg":"人工智能"},{"pid":"67abfe088b5a53006f616128d8c2c6ff01c6e9c8","tid":545441,"uid":36084,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:05:31.000Z","msg":"明眼人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f393647d619c55829b1fec7519b7717cb3bf4a7","tid":545441,"uid":155818,"like":82,"dislike":1,"score":81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:08:02.000Z","msg":"上面張神偷圖真係見一次笑一次"},{"pid":"4f04db8df6955bc94a9bd5da4f3e8232e0325062","tid":545441,"uid":76488,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:08:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e89d2608a4408f7855491dd74a7432387e8805ce","tid":545441,"uid":46965,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:15:26.000Z","msg":"又係你呀陳生"},{"pid":"c328ecfc72f88782720c742013ebe72cf625b2fc","tid":545441,"uid":46013,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:16:53.000Z","msg":"年又過年"},{"pid":"574b74152a87f6d2c2ca956e460897bfee5a850d","tid":545441,"uid":3602,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T17:08:43.000Z","msg":"明眼人"},{"pid":"c0e47b279148dbc421cbf1a1fe30c11d15c2f7f0","tid":545441,"uid":137627,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T17:11:38.000Z","msg":"又黎欺凌呀，大人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8fa38641a7b41129ec96f5ca9aa0a308844a759","tid":545441,"uid":83748,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T18:59: